<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>View Post</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/forumPost.css">
</head>
<body>

    <main>
        <article class="post">
            <h2 class="post-title">Keeping cooking simple</h2>
            <div class="post-content">
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6d/Good_Food_Display_-_NCI_Visuals_Online.jpg/800px-Good_Food_Display_-_NCI_Visuals_Online.jpg" alt="Food" class="post-image">
                <p class="post-text">
                    Food is a very important part of everyone's life. If you want to be healthy, you have to eat healthy. One of the easiest way to do that is to keep your cooking nice and simple.
                </p>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="comments">
                <h3>Comments</h3>

            </div>
            <form action="#" method="POST" class="comment-form">
                <textarea name="comment" id="comment" rows="3" placeholder="Write a comment..."></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Post Comment</button>
            </form>
        </article>
    </main>

</body>
</html>